  "time_ut": 1662379120,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da0\u0dd3\u0db1\u0dba\u0da7 \u0db7\u0dd6\u0db8\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca:13\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "An earthquake in China: 13 dead",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Foreign media reported that 13 people died in an earthquake that occurred in Sichuan Province, China.",
        "The earthquake occurred at around 1 pm today (05) Chinese time.",
        "The strength of the earthquake was recorded as 6.8 on the Richter scale.",
        "Foreign media said that due to the earthquake, telephone lines have collapsed in Sichuan province and landslides have also occurred.",
        "Chinese authorities said this was the worst earthquake to hit Sichuan province since 2017.",
        "Chinese media reported that relief workers have already been deployed to remove the soil that fell on the roads due to the landslides.",
        "Chinese media reported that houses in Sichuan province were also damaged due to the earthquake."
      ],
